Finister, C., Pollet, T. V., & Neave, N. (2021). An exploratory factor analysis of the Nerdy Personality Attributes Scale in a sample of self-identified nerds/geeks. The Social Science Journal, 1-9. This week is related to critiquing. First read both articles and then pick one to critique, in particular scrutinize the measures used and use what we’ve covered in the course as your justifications. #nerds
